  <official_title>Multicenter, Phase 2 Clinical Trial Evaluating the Efficacy and Tolerability of Induction and Consolidation Chemotherapy Comprising Fludarabine, Cytarabine, and Attenuated-dose Idarubicin in Elderly Patients With AML(Acute Myeloid Leukemia)</official_title>
