  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A phase II clinical trial evaluating the efficacy and tolerability of induction and
      consolidation chemotherapy comprising Fludarabine, cytarabine and attenuated-dose Idarubicin
      (modified-FLAI) in the elderly patients with acute myeloid leukemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
